nodes.text: The Syboona smuggler Knire Dark owned a storehouse that she used for storing her illegal merchandise. It was raided by Galactic Republic authorities around 22 BBY, ending Dark's career. The raid was chronicled in HoloNet News Vol. 531 49, an issue of the HoloNet News, that was released during the same year of the incident. Due to Dark's attachment to Podracing, the article noted that the event, along with several other Podracing related incidents, called for the sport of Podracing to be heavily scrutinized.
The storehouse was first mentioned in an issue of the HoloNet News. It was mentioned again under Knire Dark's entry in 2008's The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia.
